{"tid":1463270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真正嘅弱點係進出機場嘅流量","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:00:09.000Z","uid":37894,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"564c073db2ede744b57b9bf41f04bc982e2f307b","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"佢地琴日取消航班係因為入機場同離開機場嘅流量爆左，好似我地有data但又上唔到網咁。<br />\n<br />\n今次運動嘅重點係機場交通，大家留喺機場係唔夠，琴日停飛喺主因唔係堵塞，係流量。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該不停進出機場，用盡機場交通嘅流量，令入機場嘅人排大隊，想離開嘅人因排隊走而滯留，等多d人被迫留機場或者上唔到機。<br />\n<br />\n我地出入機場合情合法合法，就可以隊爆機場嘅交通流量。又唔洗同人衝突。"},{"pid":"2a0303bfb266ab8a9c60e9d4bb235c2478783c31","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"5d58496d4f8f6872d913f650683bf9d1fadf9240","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"大家行動丫"},{"pid":"de7dd393250efe391766ca7d1890013f7b978b32","tid":1463270,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7a5a3fbba56b5a721026c2d397dfc492ec49e0","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"唔需要塞閘口"},{"pid":"36881a757fe53b3cbf8f083dc9d450e6b54febfe","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"排隊搭車"},{"pid":"15fd951a4bf0f547891fd2fbdceee1d67e66e0dd","tid":1463270,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"174687914055f0c4b90c1c789d6cb40307706ba9","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"E車A車都可以搭"},{"pid":"6ab3a60f364ff736808022d33f43a7c7b975815a","tid":1463270,"uid":63770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep