"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"d83a4f60d54b113d703cb4f2536ffb1ed42c2434","tid":1463270,"uid":127704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"19baadf38d4893407000462c36f4cf9beb921691","tid":1463270,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"353147640bd464d4d337eeb54ccc0ff6f9b0d656","tid":1463270,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></strong><br />\n但大家要記得塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></strong>去拉埋大陸攬炒<br />\n<br />\n建議集中火力<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搵出影響力最大</span></strong></span>&amp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最多人能響應</span></span></strong>嘅時間，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">eg六/日</span></span></strong>形式塞爆<br />\n<br />\n能節省大家金錢外同時能<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong>但又能為香港帶來巨額經濟損失(謹記損失每日獨立計算)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/